        <p class="light-gray">
          As you enter your 40s, oily skin often becomes more reactive, with increased sensitivity and lingering
          redness. Aging skin also faces environmental stress, hormonal fluctuations, and oxidative damage—all
          contributing to irritation and inflammation. This NicholsMD skincare routine is expertly designed to reduce
          redness, manage oil production, and protect against visible signs of aging, helping you maintain a healthy,
          balanced glow.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="result__first__row">
        <div class="result__description__container">
          <p class="light-gray">Your Essential Skincare Set for Oily Skin</p>
          <br>
          <br>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Clear Daily Soothing UV Defense SPF</strong><br>
                Provide your skin with daily protection against harmful UV rays using this lightweight, non-comedogenic
                sunscreen. It calms redness and prevents sun-induced irritation while maintaining a shine-free, smooth
                complexion.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Gentle Cleanser</strong><br>
                Cleanse your skin effectively without disrupting its natural moisture barrier. This soothing, gentle
                formula removes excess oil, pollutants, and makeup while calming sensitive, redness-prone skin.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto A+ Brightening Treatment Serum</strong><br>
                Combat redness and improve skin tone with this oil-free, brightening serum. Formulated with azelaic acid
                and calming botanicals, it visibly reduces blotchiness and refines texture for smoother,
                healthier-looking skin.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Silymarin CF by SkinCeuticals</strong><br>
                Strengthen your skin’s defenses against aging and environmental aggressors with this high-potency
                vitamin C serum. Specially designed for oily skin, it reduces oil oxidation, calms inflammation, and
                minimizes visible redness, all while helping to prevent breakouts.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Gel</strong><br>
                Soothe and hydrate with this calming botanical gel, ideal for oily, sensitive skin. Enriched with
                hyaluronic acid, cucumber, and thyme, it provides a cooling effect that reduces visible redness and
                hydrates without adding weight.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Essence Mist</strong><br>
                Instantly refresh and calm your skin on the go with this lightweight mist. It hydrates, strengthens the
                skin barrier, and helps reduce redness and irritation throughout the day.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Redness Neutralizer</strong><br>
                Complete your regimen with this advanced redness treatment that targets the underlying causes of
                inflammation. Formulated with biomimetic peptides and soothing plant extracts, it minimizes redness and
                supports long-term skin calmness and resilience.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
